JumpI SubPrintCalResultToDisplay 
/ Add local variables of SubPrintCalResultToDisplay here (if any)

///
/// You may define your constants here
///
ZERO, DEC 0

/ Global variables shared between subroutines
Operand1,  DEC 0        / first operand value
Operand2,  DEC 0        / second operand value
Operator,  DEC 0        / operator character code (+, -, *, /)
CalResult, DEC 0        / result of the calculation

/ Character constants (Unicode values)
CharPlus,   DEC 43      / '+'
CharMinus,  DEC 45      / '-'
CharMul,    DEC 42      / '*'
CharDiv,    DEC 47      / '/'
CharEquals, DEC 61      / '='
CharZero,   DEC 48      / '0'


/ Here are some data labels that are useful for testing the code.
ONE, DEC 1
PIXELOFROW2COL2, HEX 0F11 
SIXTYFOUR, DEC 64
NEXTDIGIT, DEC 15

